name: Mark Cuckerberg #1
description: Mark is the kind of guy that had no friends, so he had to build a platform off of other people’s ideas. Even though it’s currently one of the most used social media platforms, he somehow still manages to be one of the most despised human beings on the face of this book (no pun intended). Btw, Facebook fucking blows and everything you touch (Mark), turns to shit. Twitter (@crypto_wook)
